title: SXSW 2019: "Good Omens"
excerpt: Highlights from the red carpet of the Amazon Prime show "Good Omens" at the ZACH Theatre during SXSW. Stars Michael Sheen, Jon Hamm and David Tennant spoke t...
description: Michael Sheen: The story really is about this angel and this demon. A demon who’s not quite as mean and evil as he would like to think he is, and an angel who’s not quite as good as he would like to think he is. I think the more time they spend together the more they start to rub off on each other, I think that says a lot of about us. It’s our flaws and it’s our imperfections that make us who we are.
